  "title": "Assistant Manufacturing Engineer (Semiconductor Automation / East)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Responsible for machine setup, module alignment, vision\nalignment/calibration, and machine checkout.</p><p>• Provide occasional on-site support, both locally and internationally.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• NITEC, Higher NITEC, or Diploma in Engineering.</p><p>• At least 1 year of relevant experience.</p><p>• Proficiency in machinery automation, including electrical, servo, sensor, and pneumatic systems.</p><p>• Ability to read mechanical and electrical drawings is advantageous.</p><p>• Experience in mechanical alignment, motor tuning, or vision systems is a plus.</p><p>• Positive attitude and willingness to take on additional responsibilities as needed.</p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">To find out more about this opportunity, please contact <strong>Lionel Liew </strong>at <strong>lionel.liew@gmprecruit.com</strong>.</a></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>GMP Technologies (S) Pte Ltd   |   EA Licence: 11C3793 |   EA Personnel: Lionel Liew   |   Registration No: R1330693</p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>This is in partnership with the Employment and Employability Institute Pte Ltd (“e2i”).</em></a></p><p><em>e2i is the empowering network for workers and employers seeking employment and employability solutions. e2i serves as a bridge between workers and employers, connecting\nwith workers to offer job security through job-matching, career guidance and\nskills upgrading services, and partnering employers to address their manpower\nneeds through recruitment, training, and job redesign solutions. e2i is a\ntripartite initiative of the National Trades Union Congress set up to support\nnation-wide manpower and skills upgrading initiatives.</em></p><p><em>By applying for this role, you consent to GMP Technologies (S) Pte Ltd’s </em><a href=\"https://www.gmprecruit.com/legal/privacy-policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>PDPA</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"https://us-west-2.protection.sophos.com?d=e2i.com.sg&u=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZTJpLmNvbS5zZy9wZHBhLw==&i=NThlNDdhOGMyYmI5N2YwZmQxZDk4NjQw&t=cWdqRFV0Uy80RjN3MDlSYmM1dS85VTRxVTRoYVlXdWFyWTYzaGlVS3k0TT0=&h=1ad0460f503340658fbeab159c31256f&s=AVNPUEhUT0NFTkNSWVBUSVaVGQEVMuPAipiPENS4aadnRg3RqoiWpHBKgNtumWhHjA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>e2i’s PDPA</em></a><em>.</em></p>",
